\#\# Accessibility Requirements  
\`\`\`  
Color Contrast:  
├─ Text Primary on Surface Primary: 16:1 (AAA)  
├─ Text Secondary on Surface Primary: 7:1 (AA)  
├─ Text Tertiary on Surface Secondary: 4.5:1 (AA)  
└─ Interactive elements: Minimum 3:1 (AA)

Keyboard Navigation:  
├─ Tab order: Logical, left-to-right, top-to-bottom  
├─ Focus visible: Always (custom ring, never hidden)  
├─ Skip links: "Skip to results", "Skip to synthesis"  
└─ Escape key: Close modals, reset focus

Screen Reader:  
├─ Semantic HTML: \<section\>, \<article\>, \<nav\>  
├─ ARIA labels: For icon-only buttons  
├─ ARIA live regions: For real-time updates (sliders)  
├─ Alt text: For charts (describe data trends)  
└─ Table headers: \<th\> with scope attributes

Motion:  
├─ Respect prefers-reduced-motion  
├─ If reduced: Transitions become instant (0ms)  
├─ Animations: Optional, not critical to understanding  
└─ Skeleton loading: Still visible but static

